short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirects GoToMeeting meeting urls to the web client version

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Forces GoToMeeting to use the web client, redirecting an url like this:

https://www.gotomeeting.com/join/123456789

To this:

https://app.gotomeeting.com/?meetingId=123456789
